            <p class="post-heading"> Best of Games 2022 from IGN India: God of War: Ragnarok, Elden Ring and Call of Duty: MW2 were the Highlights of the year </p>
            <span>BY: IGN INDIA </span> <span style="margin-left:20px">PUBLISHED: DEC 29, 2022 </span>
        </div>
    
        <div class="post-body">
            <div class="highlight-body">
                <div class="upper-highlight">
                    <img src="/images/highlights/ign-ind.jpg" alt="" class="highlight-img-top">
                </div>
                <div class="lower-highlight">
                    <span class="para-1">It is that time of the year when we summarize all the best games that came out in 2022. It was a fantastic year for games as we received a range of titles, including some top-of-the-line flagship games across all platforms. <br><br> It was not only a good year for console and PC players, but the mobile gaming players also got some good games.</span>
                    <p class="para-2">2022 saw some monumental events in gaming. Players saw games like Modern Warfare 2 and God of War: Ragnarok smashing all the records set by previous games in their respective franchises. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
                <p class="para-3">We saw many Indie games taking on the biggest flagship titles of the year. The Best games of 2022 from IGN India list contains games that we felt were the best out of all the games we reviewed in 2022. Some of you might agree with the games in this list, and some might not. Regardless, this can also serve as a recommendation or discovery resource for gamers. Now, let’s get straight into it.</p>

